data.description: Welcome to Camden Cove. This stunning 3bd with a bonus room, 2ba home is ready to welcome you with open arms. When you enter the home, you can’t help but notice the architectural details like bay window, tray ceilings, arches throughout and plenty of windows for natural light. The Master suite bathroom has everything you love with walk-in closet, double vanity sink, separate walk-in shower & garden tub. Kitchen has a cozy breakfast nook overlooking the backyard and includes a pantry. The perfect privacy fenced backyard backs up to a wooded area, has plenty of space with mature trees and a covered patio with ceiling fans. The fence has a double gate that’s convenient for parking extra vehicles. Camden Cove is one of Calera's most desired communities with community pool, playground, walking trail and perfect convenience to I-65, Hwy 31 and shopping/restaurants. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home!
